{"tid":1586782,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【鍵戰/ 晒你幾秒】TVB食屎啦，每日洗版任務 - 滴露","createTime":"2019-09-22T06:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:13:08.000Z","uid":113630,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2f5a459509060b101a63015657b1e75572acc93e","tid":1586782,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:29:44.000Z","msg":"今日A餐巴出咗街，我開咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有TVB員工透露：</span></span></strong> <br />\n<blockquote>真係TVB做，睇住佢廣告量係少左4成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Prime time 係得返好多無錢收自家promo，大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB係品牌負資產，連員工都唔撐！</span></span>#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#dog <br />\nTVB下個月開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到年底啦！ 廣告界多返強調，去FB洗版係有用ga</strong> <br />\n<br />\n本身我屋企都成日用滴露消毒，但滴露竟然喺TVB落廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 消委會話滴露潔手液多防腐劑，用佢潔手液洗手又等於沾上黑警殺人既血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，都係轉用威路士/小曼家族好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70818401_457223125134542_1545761942465937408_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_oc=AQlGgiKjV5af3_3Gf62YZjNnFPv8yBdE9rxfwzfjGnC6IzQxuB6fzsMcribWzFf-c6g&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=26117b9cabd6d8d9209caabc21ae4105&amp;oe=5E38EAD8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70818401_457223125134542_1545761942465937408_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_oc%3DAQlGgiKjV5af3_3Gf62YZjNnFPv8yBdE9rxfwzfjGnC6IzQxuB6fzsMcribWzFf-c6g%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D26117b9cabd6d8d9209caabc21ae4105%26oe%3D5E38EAD8&h=dac2a7fa&s={SIZE}\" />   <br />\n【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】 1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n是日精選@22 Sep 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>滴露</strong></span></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dettolhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdettolhk&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=9d43fb57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dettolhk</a></span></strong>   <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請用幾秒</span></strong>去派嬲、留言、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得?</span></strong>  <br />\n<br />\n <strong>※留言template，二擇其一，歡迎創意留言。</strong> <br />\n1️⃣ 無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n 2️⃣ 我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！  <br />\n<br />\n   <img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71033627_457226428467545_3099959582953308160_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQm1DM_avAUNadpkKmW2j61lve95BkTSlruUmZ2yGNIWGC7dGmDPZl8A4d72Ql2z7Bw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=65bbe41ff6095d8c06223c33336bda60&amp;oe=5E31EDE4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71033627_457226428467545_3099959582953308160_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQm1DM_avAUNadpkKmW2j61lve95BkTSlruUmZ2yGNIWGC7dGmDPZl8A4d72Ql2z7Bw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D65bbe41ff6095d8c06223c33336bda60%26oe%3D5E31EDE4&h=5db19b1e&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">已經更新</span>: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span> <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=5fd7f590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a>  <br />\n －－－－－－－ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=2c0e905f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb <br />\nTG 抵制廣告行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=6876761b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a> <br />\nTG 狙擊綜合頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2cctvb[/quote]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2cctvb%5B%2Fquote%5D&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=465ee29a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2cctvb[/quote]</a>"},{"pid":"1e404f7af492086513dd1ec776296d051d7bafdc","tid":1586782,"uid":113630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T06:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7473f02ab7e3517dede313ef3e6dadd0cd51c5a","tid":1586782,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT